Geocoding.FromAddressToPoint - Class in eu.trentorise.smartcampus.osm.android.util
This class contains an AsyncTask that permits to convert an Address into a GeoPoint You have to allocate a new AsyncTask like this:
Geocoding.FromAddressToPoint myTask = new Geocoding.FromAddressToPoint(context);
myTask.execute(String address);
GeoPoint result = myTask.get();

This class contains an AsyncTask that permits to convert a GeoPoint into an Address You have to allocate a new AsyncTask like this:
